Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借着盛典开幕之初
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我向我们二年A班全体同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就设置圣诞树挂灯等准备工作中 所作出的努力表示衷心的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 很感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满怀着对提供帮助的同学以及莅临来宾的感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣布 第五十七届创设祭现在正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来看我啊 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的演讲很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞树很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是大家的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:54.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,240)\fad(150,150)}绚辻词编
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:54.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,290)\fad(150,150)}最终章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:54.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,340)\fad(150,150)}约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学 快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟弥生她们约好了有空一起到处逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学要一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 待会见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要鸡蛋和鱼糕是吧 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的小白兔 我要吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请饶了我吧 鲨鱼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下来7号选手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝉联两届圣诞女郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家翘首以待的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森岛遥学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆 好大胆的尺寸啊 森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这服装符合要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我看来 这在许可范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥突然想参赛我只好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 看她这么高兴就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 多 多 关 照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来森岛学姐是众望所归啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她长得漂亮啊 蝉联三届应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学也认为获胜的是森岛学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢 大家都很可爱 我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 弥生 我还有执行委员的工作 要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝会上见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要点心 我要点心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急 点心一人有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 别乱碰其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要把手伸进里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗 真受小孩子欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这甜酒看起来味道不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不会给老师你喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不至于因为去年醉酒略微失态而这样对我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一杯而已 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有惨事发生的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便巡视一下 毕竟跟你约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺兴旺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一也喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶还是甜米酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了 马上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们在等着你的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉纯一 我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学 为什么会变成那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒不坏  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 为何我还闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请三思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使今年交不到女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不着放火那么激进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是小学时代收到的情信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么现在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得喜欢谁或讨厌谁是一件羞耻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我硬起心肠不予回复
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来真是后悔莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到总不能一直懊悔下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆把它烧成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是万分后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 大将
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说过今年要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜还没结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其在自怨自哀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如积极行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别像我那样留下遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么交不到女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲哭无泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 绚辻同学送我礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面是糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至此 第57届创设祭完满结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心感谢各位的莅临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您有个美好的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为第57届创设祭的完满结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢 这都是大家的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 是绚辻同学努力的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很忙 但很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备祭典的时候是最快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容易啊 这样就结束倒有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 主持人做得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也想穿上圣诞装参赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 今年森岛学姐漂亮地蝉联
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去打工来担任司仪也有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 庆祝会已经开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮演的圣诞老人很受大家欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 绚辻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没跟大家正式道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回教室去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原 你好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但主角一般都最后登场的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创设祭几乎看不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点俗务要办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又被甩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 橘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也对橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对圣诞节有段痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很怕这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年也因逃避 没能参加创设祭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我知道不能这样一直下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是希望当上执行委员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今年圣诞克服心魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就与绚辻同学一同工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我捡到绚辻同学记事本的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还被你带到神社
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梦都没想到绚辻同学竟然有这样的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能知道真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在绚辻同学的训斥下工作 虽然忙得不可开交
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但每天都过的很充实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种愉悦让我觉得圣诞节不再可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连对圣诞的恐惧也快要消失似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 从那时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜欢上绚辻同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌…现在的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢现在的绚辻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前倔强的绚辻同学也好 装乖的绚辻同学也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 别说不在这些伤感的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我还有不足 你就训斥我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的就是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才让“自己”消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的那个绚辻还健在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这声音是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才从这里发出很大的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我喝甜米酒喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踉踉跄跄跌倒了 不禁发出叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊动了你真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 田中老师 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作我送给你们的圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也想要男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我想高桥老师首先要节制一下喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面抱住女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是性骚扰啊 性骚扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些往事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天 我得知圣诞老人是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个事实就摆在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像大家常说的 看到父母放下礼物的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的情况更为糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢 知道了圣诞老人不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那时候就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己成为圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不能成为真正的圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想能够做圣诞老人做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞老人做的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在平安夜 给大家送上幸福作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为此而担任执行委员的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的力量 能让大家度过一个更加幸福的圣诞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多么美好的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候 我参加了辉东高中创设祭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我就想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭自己双手举办一次创设祭 会不会让大家感到幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家幸福的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已变质成单纯的自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但连小孩子都看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮演的圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽受大人欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却不得孩子欢心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连绚辻同学也骗不了小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下年还有下下年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节还会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候再让大家感到幸福不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你也能给我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是女性说的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我自己能弄好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…喜欢橘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不再离开你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是契约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是呦~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 就这点事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满爸爸妈妈回忆的树
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在这里 爸爸跟妈妈许下了重要的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:22:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揪~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝愿世界上每个人 在这佳节里都能感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我们那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.88,0:25:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.93,0:25:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 有事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有一天 一个素未谋面的可爱女孩跟你表白你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.30,0:25:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.29,0:25:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管啦 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.10,0:25:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.42,0:25:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的女孩向我表白我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.25,0:25:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对她毫不了解的话 也不能贸然答应
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.33,0:25:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哥哥来说真是周到的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.35,0:25:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.05,0:25:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个冬日我被甩的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.98,0:25:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将再现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

